[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating dynamic access options**\n\nI'm looking at potential ways to call a function directly using reflection on a package-private level, which might be better to avoid issues with ClassLoader status. I need to consider how to cover Method.invoke as well, since it looks like it requires metadata for invokeOnThread too. Using public invoke might be fine, but I’m wondering about the ClassLoader assertion in native code—hmm, that's a bit tricky!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b8a85f28743fd750169f97f3c676881a2950cd5ca619c1a81\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-X9HbciWBTHwBzmGdybIbQgMWu_1oCKaO2GgIrUX-_YeWkLL4BkC5_wT6HCOuhPki5cY15yjIb9TVY1vA6RFitOuHg6eyTm-D-nrUKImVmFSeamfgJ9-5GuCJvaErILNqaX1QZS7LIRz08Nf449HlJJkRntc-oexLgAgrsHyk6VoN3c0XrGpdUqqWQj2luEFK6-LNInUwLjwPbEH5pu4QRlDLcG7ChhJxdhzLxQIkXmy7CqRQf6cOgheQyCZH7ov_9uOFL1griYFNFk-uW0vvruyxygkAd2bVsEj1UJEUDO0ik_FAb0TW5Bnihz5JvHpYfvreUcykZCyO6y0CVm-bStV2VVWCFI5vzACaYfJgkIHr74Ura_5-wJAYGAbfm2qCDN3nYBigBbsuqMZalvx4N0nSzJ1209KcClWvOH9MztZMiwxKHfxLE1uyEGlO3zLui3nTPU3xvlmyww_YWwQ6Lixj2Sj1tO6oacD6wkZLoobbNVX8bxcVq0ORCxz5Eca4KBd48NIryBp9b7NpoysfSwS6v0m9oD7qHL-rUfE1lEqSDExeMEKr-1fRb4pG2szZEXgUDLsKZub3EO2MI2PUs8FOA6WD9kun6gW2RvPiafIJ4KfDS7eqKuTVarC4mcDfpqWeGd-nEebVYxDbBesnM9IsP2FeNnyfYiSoKPgaSsQRoSN-OJWZ-BNJuf26k58tmgdB1lTbPbOm4giY-RYWkh5p6uewnb2j3pRtJQN4e4GPC4C4Jcl495Ms7YyolmK0RJIdjTSzhqF9SLPghChNOP50gdkdn4a_kgKsFOaWdFk7CjWm0qpZRASuPlw72uwwfEESLjX4sSW-HJdAhh6LmOMc6IKdyjjBYnjlMcH8hhNeRLJevL8ZOkVTCgR4Ihyr14GYJY8nX_l3Znai33_UL-F9-UVHNIRuWZn5mYgrbJUrWyOLlyBN9709XW1R-8uFg96TjMW1iJ1I2S9sOUiaen-0HN8GDz65xBQSesyU2ByNL7fJH7oAnYYotpr6MXT4eOUehkjOrtcsFTReEgMOH2ig2ulHAVA3iOQWxz5leQzHCh_QD1ABibQPhQX8NY0G64Z4oo3PIsbhw85dvPxU8NUVbGJJfjqFu5-mXnX1Cpo8bo5hDM5f8zr3flF08a75S7kjj79s24y8ngeEWgewcIkixUYGRCldeGx19GvVwQvg3U0b_x4nH6XphrK_Ai8AHGSIK5O4-ss3FOCQQQmCXzLgXYKGImV5bIppVBW4Kii5cgxCv1Vch1kcW0O8ZjK12C0pN3NxPkI